issues.title: Login Broken
issues.body:
https://www.google.com/accounts/ClientLogin has been deprecated.

https://developers.google.com/identity/protocols/AuthForInstalledApps denotes that OAuth 2.0 migration is required.

commit.message:
Cleaning up and mavenizing the project

ChangeLog:
   - disabled a few tests that are mostly failing because the JSON string
   isn't an exact match (ie. ordering is breaking things )
   - removed javadoc folder.  mvn javadoc:javadoc if you need it.
     (though it needs some polish )

Synching Source with master branch

 - This should now be in sync with the latest from https://code.google.com/archive/p/google-voice-java/.
   We should now be generating the exact same code in both maven and ant
   branches.

maven branch: added json source files
